			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><h1>Au sommaire du numéro 19 de XY Mag</h1>
<p>TELECHARGEMENT DIRECT DE L&#8217;EPISODE PAR BLIP TV : <a href="http://blip.tv/file/get/Xymagpodcast-XYMagNumero19HD527.mp">Clique droit sur ce lien et enregistrer</a></p>
<ul>
<li>La PS VITA</li>
<li>ILIFE avec Iphoto, Garageband, Imovie</li>
<li>Unit 13 pour PS VITA</li>
</ul>
<p>Par XY Mag le podcast vidéo</p>
<div class="shr-publisher-1268"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class='shareaholic-like-buttonset' style='float:right;height:30px;'><a class='shareaholic-fblike' data-shr_layout='standard' data-shr_showfaces='false' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xymag.tv%2Fles-videos%2Fxy-mag-numero-19-hd%2F' data-shr_title='XY+Mag+num%C3%A9ro+19+HD'></a><a class='shareaholic-fbsend' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xymag.tv%2Fles-videos%2Fxy-mag-numero-19-hd%2F'></a><a class='shareaholic-googleplusone' data-shr_size='standard' data-shr_count='true' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xymag.tv%2Fles-videos%2Fxy-mag-numero-19-hd%2F' data-shr_title='XY+Mag+num%C3%A9ro+19+HD'></a><a class='shareaholic-tweetbutton' data-shr_count='none' data-shr_href='http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xymag.tv%2Fles-videos%2Fxy-mag-numero-19-hd%2F' data-shr_title='XY+Mag+num%C3%A9ro+19+HD'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic -->
