		<comments>http://www.xymag.tv/les-articles/bilan-des-articles-publies-en-2011/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 29 Dec 2011 16:22:25 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>xymagpodcast@gmail.com (XY Mag le podcast)</dc:creator>
